metadata.dcterms:title: Pine genotype data - Evolutionary Applications
metadata.dcterms:creator: Cullingham, Catherine
metadata.dcterms:description: This file contains genotyping information for lodgepole pine, and jack pine used to identify putative candidates of adaptation to further develop mountain pine beetle spread risk models
